            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/50381e1a0c7f0797/text/000001625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-50381e1a0c7f0797-5a33ed twpub-50381e1a0c7f0797-691cf8 twpub-50381e1a0c7f0797-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"c19\"><div class=\"c2\">Project Gutenberg™ eBooks are often created from several printed editions, all of which are confirmed as not protected by copyright in the U.S. unless a copyright notice is included. Thus, we do not necessarily keep eBooks in compliance with any particular paper edition.</div></div></div>"
        },
